        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Report of a scouting expedition after Indians.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>Coln <persName>Austin</persName></p>

<p>Dear Sir Agreeable to your order I Dispatchd two men <persName>Washing
Curtis</persName> and <persName>Robert Arm Strong</persName> to Examin the <placeName>countray west of this
Place</placeName> they went out a Bout 35 miles <placeName>a Bout 10 miles west</placeName> thay
came to <placeName>foot trail</placeName> Cold not asertain How many and then <placeName>10 miles
west of Curtese</placeName> they came to a <placeName>foot trail</placeName> of 15 or 20 <persName>men </persName>and <placeName>8
miles west of Curtises</placeName> thay came to a trail 15 or 20 Horses and But
one Mule track a mong them to Be Discoverd Theas Horses was
Rode By <persName>Indians </persName>as thay Traild them to whar thay Got Down and
Drank all theas Trail was Traveling near a N :W Cours I Have
just Receivd news of <persName>king Caid</persName> and <persName>Furn Ashes</persName> Horses all Being
Stolen   all this Sign appears To Be 2 or 3 Days oald</p>

<p>I Hope you will Take Some affective measures</p>

<p><persName>Bartlett Sims</persName></p>

<p><persName>Coln Austin</persName></p>


        </div1>
    </body>
